text: Alexandros Karageorgiou is a Greek archer. He was born on 3 June 1986. Karageorgiou competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Alexandros KarageorgiouAlexandros KARAGEORGIOU == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Greek archers Category:Olympians for Greece
